<br>
There are probably 20 to 30 guilds with clerics at various stages of their epic quest.  On top of that, Golems proved that you could do it without being in a guild.  How in the world are you ever going to create and enforce a rotation system that is fair to big guilds, mid-sized guilds, small guilds, and independents?<br>
<br>
